    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a well-cared-for car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today! It drives beautifully and has plenty of life left in it. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin. I'd love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have! \u2728",
