    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition both inside and out. The exterior retains a brilliant shine, with only minor, age-appropriate cosmetic marks that do not detract from its overall presence. The interior is exceptionally clean, featuring well-preserved upholstery and a smoke-free cabin where every button and feature operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has been serviced regularly with high-quality components, ensuring a smooth, responsive driving experience. All major maintenance is up to date, including recent fluid changes and a thorough inspection. This is a reliable, turn-key example that strikes the perfect balance between a daily driver and a cherished weekend car.",
